<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nouveau message de contact</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .site-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-left: 6px;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            color: #2d2d33;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        .info-section {
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #86868b;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 3px solid #667eea;
        }
        .info-value.email {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .message-box {
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin-top: 8px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            white-space: pre-wrap;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }
        .attachments {
            margin-top: 24px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
        }
        .attachment-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .attachment-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .attachment-info {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .attachment-name {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }
        .attachment-size {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #86868b;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }
        .metadata {
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding-top: 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e7;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .metadata-item {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 150px;
        }
        .metadata-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            color: #86868b;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .metadata-value {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f5f5f7;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #86868b;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 24px 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>📬 Nouveau message de contact</h1>
            <p>
                Vous avez reçu un nouveau message depuis votre formulaire de contact
                {% if siteName is defined and siteName %}
                    <span class="site-badge">{{ siteName }}</span>
                {% endif %}
                {% if siteUrl is defined and siteUrl %}
                    <br>
                    <a href="{{ siteUrl }}" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); text-decoration: underline;">{{ siteUrl }}</a>
                {% endif %}
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-label">Expéditeur</div>
                <div class="info-value email">{{ sender }}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-label">Sujet</div>
                <div class="info-value">{{ subject }}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-label">Message</div>
                <div class="message-box">{{ content }}</div>
            </div>
            
            {% if attachments is defined and attachments|length > 0 %}
            <div class="attachments">
                <div class="info-label">Pièces jointes ({{ attachments|length }})</div>
                {% for attachment in attachments %}
                <div class="attachment-item">
                    <div class="attachment-icon">📎</div>
                    <div class="attachment-info">
                        <div class="attachment-name">{{ attachment.name }}</div>
                        <div class="attachment-size">{{ attachment.mime }}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            <div class="metadata">
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <div class="metadata-label">Date de réception</div>
                    <div class="metadata-value">{{ receivedAt|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <div class="metadata-label">Heure</div>
                    <div class="metadata-value">{{ receivedAt|date('H:i:s') }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="metadata-item">
                    <div class="metadata-label">IP Client</div>
                    <div class="metadata-value">{{ clientIp|default('Non disponible') }}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Ce message a été envoyé automatiquement depuis votre formulaire de contact.</p>
            <p>Pour répondre, utilisez l'adresse email de l'expéditeur ci-dessus.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
